{
  "stem": "27509.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was fully grown but paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to use his left hand to push the right hand to write.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so this disabled, he was in terms of that in itself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But apart from this physical disability, he was so poor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And yet I made-- or maybe I made a unconscious effort of becoming a particular friend of his, so much so that I was the only friend whom he invited to his home.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wouldn't have invited everybody else and for good reason.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think Bachach was his name-- Bachach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived in an attic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The parents' bedroom was divided from the rest of the living space with a curtain.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no other beds in that room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where that-- he slept, I can't say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where they slept on some sort of a so-called mattress on the floor at nighttime, which was rolled out or not, I can't say.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- the-- the bits of-- the sticks of furniture was so-- so few that it was pitiful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was obviously a-- a boy who most probably didn't have sufficient [INAUDIBLE] to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And yet he was a very, very brilliant, very capable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was part of that same class situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you just could not-- he was mindful of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was reserved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was withdrawn, knowing not only his physical disability but also his-- his-- his status disability because most probably his father had only at best temporary work with only different that here when you don't have work, you are going on the dole.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no such thing as dole in pre-war Poland or, for that matter, not much else in-- in-- in Europe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if it was, it was-- it was pitiful.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
